entry.title: osu! - fripside - only my railgun (TV Size) [Insane] 98.52%
entry.content: It' s been a long time since I last uploaded anything, so I figured I'd upload an osu! video since I don't really play any DDR/ITG anymore, plus I wanted to test video quality for future uploads. This is the OP for the To Aru Kagaku no Railgun anime, mapped by djpop. I would have liked my first osu video to be something different but this works too, I like the song and the map is nice other than that one stack of crap that I kept breaking combo on for the longest time. x_x I usually play without bg video but I turned it on for the sake of this video so viewers have something more to look at than a static background image. Edit: I actually beat my score on this today, now it's down to 4x 100 lol Beatmap: osu.ppy.sh osu!: osu.ppy.sh
